{"TopicId":63724,"ForumId":15,"TopicTitle":"[SOLVED] Angle for surface attach","CreatedByName":"brusura","CreatedById":57899,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-19T21:45:45Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"brusura","CreatedById":57899,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-19T21:45:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIf I attach those wings to this modded fuselage and they start angled at 15\u00C3\u201A\u00C2\u00B0 , is there something wrong with the collision mesh? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWith angle snap\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ezkZUTp.png\u0022 alt=\u0022ezkZUTp.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWithout angle snap\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/tYdsunT.png\u0022 alt=\u0022tYdsunT.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-02-21T22:09:03Z\u0022 title=\u002202/21/2014 10:09  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 21, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by brusura\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"brusura","CreatedById":57899,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-21T22:08:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAfter some empiric tests I found out the problem. The center of mesh was not the center I needed for the mesh, so the wing were indeed angled at 0\u00C3\u201A\u00C2\u00B0 but at wrong center of mesh\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-02-21T23:05:49Z\u0022 title=\u002202/21/2014 11:05  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 21, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by brusura\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dispatcher","CreatedById":78707,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-21T22:45:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EGlad you figured it out, as I had no idea how to help you. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"brusura","CreatedById":57899,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-21T23:05:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EEhehe \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E took me some swearing at the monitor but in the end I nailed it\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}